Request Path/subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.NetworkCloud/clusters/{clusterName}/bareMetalMachineKeySets/{bareMetalMachineKeySetName}
Operation IdBareMetalMachineKeySets_Update
Default Api Version2024-10-01-preview
Resource
